verbose_text: At 1 month post-transplantation, levels of human ALB in mouse peripheral blood were higher in the groups co-transplanted with CD34 + cells, showing a median of 302 mug/ml (Hep+ CD34 mice, range 3.63-626 mug/ml) compared to animals transplanted with Hep alone, reaching only a median of 51.1 mug/ml (range 1-171.7 mug/ml, P < 0.05) (XREF_FIG B).
